{"id": "1301378474694410350", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "843035505058906112", "author_name": "itsme_yong", "author_bot": false, "content": "大佬们，我这些角色能组几个队伍啊（刚玩半天不知道怎么配队）", "timestamp": "2024-10-31T02:53:26.810000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1301378473494970398", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-30_235046.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2619798, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1131839874132090890/1301378473494970398/Screenshot_2024-10-30_235046.png?ex=6a375226&is=6a3600a6&hm=c47fc3fa22138e70d252d8441a0bcac79af98df282e5658d67cf06ff2ed288c4&"}, {"id": "1301378474275111004", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-10-30_235056.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2712735, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1131839874132090890/1301378474275111004/Screenshot_2024-10-30_235056.png?ex=6a375226&is=6a3600a6&hm=843d0aceb9353940ac7ee66dfd5ea996cfc91adab5f98422f10ea72b1603e808&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301381301894381598", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "啟靈都還挺缺的，希萊、法洛思、鯊魚、水母吧🤔 \n四小強強化很多次了強度也不差，優化就是把蘿坦換成24\n~~然後血希強無敵，想無腦玩可以抽多點~~\n之後有凱後可以換掉法洛思\n珊很強但要很高練度，還要抽混沌的諾", "timestamp": "2024-10-31T03:04:40.867000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-10-31T03:37:37.939000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301389422356594801", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "176727766165618688", "author_name": "aku6739", "author_bot": false, "content": "隨便組 嘎嘎亂殺 等到稍微懂角色們在幹嘛 遊戲機制之後在來問吧 就像上面說的啟靈都很缺你還得慢慢解主線換抽抽抽啟靈以後才會開始有點角色間組隊的感覺", "timestamp": "2024-10-31T03:36:56.936000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1301390380201414676", "channel_id": "1131839874132090890", "type": 0, "author_id": "176727766165618688", "author_name": "aku6739", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果你要問什麼強 24重點培養 血鏈趁現在還能抽抽一抽看能不能抽高 抽24衝高啟靈也行 然後組隊你就想這兩隻是主要輸出 那你還缺坦還是補 看一下隊伍可以用誰就用誰 隨便玩就好 反正你現在這等級為什麼隊伍體感上都差不多\n\n基本上你現在就像蓋房子還在叫料架鋼筋 真的不用先想你想蓋成高樓大廈還洋房", "timestamp": "2024-10-31T03:40:45.304000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
